          ],
          "product_description": [
            {
              "value": "The Juvale Gender Reveal Voting Board adds charm and interactivity to any baby shower or gender reveal event. Featuring a classic black chalkboard design, this voting board measures 12 x 17 inches and comes with 144 heart-shaped stickers—72 pink for a girl and 72 blue for a boy. It serves as an engaging centerpiece, allowing guests to participate in a fun and memorable gender guessing game.\n\nAs the cooler months approach, bringing gatherings indoors, this gender voting board is ideal for creating a cozy and festive atmosphere. It is not only a form of entertainment but also a delightful way to involve family and friends in the anticipation of revealing a baby's gender. The easel back support ensures easy tabletop display, making it a seamless addition to your baby shower decorations.\n\nCrafted from durable cardstock material, the board is designed for repeated use without losing its visual appeal. Suitable for adults looking to add an interactive element to their celebrations, it encourages guest interaction and fosters lasting memories. The compact size allows it to fit into any event decor without overpowering the space, making it a versatile choice for both formal and casual settings.\n\nIncluded in this set is a gender voting board and 144 stickers, providing ample opportunity for guest participation. Whether used as a team boy or girl vote board, or simply as a decorative piece, the Juvale Gender Reveal Voting Board is an essential component of your event planning toolkit. Its unique design and functionality make it a valuable addition, perfect for enhancing any baby gender games or baby shower decoration.",
              "language_tag": "en_US",
              "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
            }
